## Java 21+ Modern Ozellikler
- **Records:** Immutable DTO / Value Object icin — `public record CreateOrderRequest(String customerId, List<LineItem> items) {}`
- **Sealed classes:** Domain hiyerarsisi icin — `sealed interface PaymentMethod permits CreditCard, BankTransfer, Wallet {}`
- **Pattern matching switch:** Tip kontrolu ve destructuring tek satirda — `case Rectangle(var w, var h) -> w * h;`
- **Virtual Threads:** I/O-bound islemler icin — `Thread.ofVirtual().start(task)` veya `Executors.newVirtualThreadPerTaskExecutor()`
- **Sequenced Collections:** `collection.getFirst()`, `collection.getLast()`, `collection.reversed()`
- **String Templates (preview):** `STR."Hello \{name}"` — string concat yerine; SQL injection riski SIFIR
- **Optional:** `Optional.orElseThrow()` tercih et; ASLA `Optional.get()` cagirma; field olarak KULLANMA

## Spring Boot 3 Best Practices
- **Auto-configuration:** Custom starter icin `META-INF/spring/org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.AutoConfiguration.imports`
- **Profiles:** `application.yml` + `application-{profile}.yml`; secret icin Spring Cloud Config veya Vault
- **Actuator:** `/actuator/health`, `/actuator/metrics`, `/actuator/info` — production'da sensitive endpoint'leri kilitle
- **Bean Validation:** `@Valid` + `jakarta.validation` — `@NotNull`, `@Size`, `@Pattern`; custom constraint yazarak domain kurallarini enforce et
- **GraalVM Native:** `spring-boot-starter-parent` 3.x ile native image destegi; reflection-heavy kutuphanelere dikkat
- **Properties binding:** `@ConfigurationProperties(prefix = "app.order")` + `@EnableConfigurationProperties` — `@Value` yerine tip-guvenli binding
- **Startup:** `@EventListener(ApplicationReadyEvent.class)` — is mantigi `@PostConstruct`'ta CALISTIRMA

## Spring Data JPA / Hibernate 6
- **Entity mapping:** `@Entity` + `@Table`; Id stratejisi: `@GeneratedValue(strategy = IDENTITY)` veya UUID
- **Audit:** `@EntityListeners(AuditingEntityListener.class)` + `@CreatedDate`, `@LastModifiedDate`
- **N+1 onleme:** `@EntityGraph(attributePaths = {"items"})` veya `JOIN FETCH` JPQL; ASLA lazy load'a guvenme
- **Projections:** Interface-based projection veya DTO projection (`new OrderSummary(o.id, o.status)` JPQL) — entity donme (read-only icin)
- **Batch insert:** `spring.jpa.properties.hibernate.jdbc.batch_size=50` + `@BatchSize`
- **Read-only:** `@Transactional(readOnly = true)` — Hibernate dirty check devre disi, performans artisi
- **Repository:** Spring Data `JpaRepository<T, ID>` + custom query method naming; karmasik sorgular icin `@Query` veya Specification pattern
- **Optimistic locking:** `@Version` ile concurrent update koruması — pessimistic lock ASLA default olmasin

```java
@Entity
@Table(name = "orders")
@EntityListeners(AuditingEntityListener.class)
public class Order {
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)
    private Long id;

    @Column(nullable = false)
    private String customerId;

    @Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
    private OrderStatus status = OrderStatus.PENDING;

    @OneToMany(mappedBy = "order", cascade = CascadeType.ALL, orphanRemoval = true)
    private List<OrderItem> items = new ArrayList<>();

    @Version
    private Long version;

    @CreatedDate
    private Instant createdAt;

    public void addItem(OrderItem item) {
        items.add(item);
        item.setOrder(this);
    }
}
```

## Hexagonal / Clean Architecture (Spring Uyarlamasi)
```
domain/           -> Entity, Value Object, Domain Event, Port (interface)
                     SIFIR Spring bagimliligi. Sadece Java SE.
application/      -> Use Case (service), Input/Output Port, DTO, Mapper
                     Sadece domain'e bagimli. Spring stereotype (@Service) sadece burada.
adapter/
├── in/web/       -> @RestController, Request/Response DTO, validation
├── in/messaging/ -> @RabbitListener, Kafka consumer
├── out/persistence/ -> @Repository (JPA impl), JPA Entity, Mapper
└── out/client/   -> WebClient/RestClient, external API adapter
config/           -> @Configuration, @Bean, DI wiring, Security config
```
- **Port:** Domain'deki interface — `OrderRepository`, `NotificationSender`
- **Adapter:** Infrastructure implementasyonu — `JpaOrderRepository implements OrderRepository`
- **ASLA** controller'da is mantigi; controller → use case → domain

## Async ve Virtual Threads (Project Loom)
- **Virtual Threads:** `spring.threads.virtual.enabled=true` (Spring Boot 3.2+) — tum Tomcat handler'lari virtual thread'de calisir
- **CompletableFuture:** Paralel cagrilar icin — `CompletableFuture.allOf(f1, f2).join()`
- **@Async:** `@EnableAsync` + `@Async("taskExecutor")` — donus tipi `CompletableFuture<T>` OLMALI; `void` KULLANMA
- **WebClient:** Non-blocking HTTP client; `RestTemplate` deprecated — `RestClient` (Spring 6.1) senkron alternatif
- **Structured Concurrency (preview):** `StructuredTaskScope.ShutdownOnFailure` — child task lifecycle yonetimi

```java
// Virtual thread executor (Spring Boot 3.2+ otomatik, elle de tanimlanabilir)
@Bean
public ExecutorService virtualThreadExecutor() {
    return Executors.newVirtualThreadPerTaskExecutor();
}
```

## Test (JUnit 5 + Spring Boot Test)
- **Unit test:** `@ExtendWith(MockitoExtension.class)` + `@Mock` + `@InjectMocks`
- **Integration test:** `@SpringBootTest` + `@Testcontainers` — gercek DB, gercek Redis
- **Slice test:** `@WebMvcTest` (controller), `@DataJpaTest` (repository) — hizli, izole
- **MockMvc:** REST endpoint testi; `mockMvc.perform(post("/api/orders").content(...)).andExpect(status().isCreated())`
- **Testcontainers:** `@Container static PostgreSQLContainer<?> pg = new PostgreSQLContainer<>("postgres:16")`
- **Test naming:** `should_ReturnOrder_When_ValidIdProvided` veya `givenValidId_whenGetOrder_thenReturnsOrder`
- **Test data:** Builder pattern veya `@Sql` ile; production seed KULLANMA

```java
@SpringBootTest
@Testcontainers
class OrderServiceIntegrationTest {
    @Container
    static PostgreSQLContainer<?> postgres = new PostgreSQLContainer<>("postgres:16-alpine");

    @DynamicPropertySource
    static void configureProperties(DynamicPropertyRegistry registry) {
        registry.add("spring.datasource.url", postgres::getJdbcUrl);
        registry.add("spring.datasource.username", postgres::getUsername);
        registry.add("spring.datasource.password", postgres::getPassword);
    }

    @Autowired
    private OrderService orderService;

    @Test
    void should_CreateOrder_When_ValidRequest() {
        var request = new CreateOrderRequest("CUST-001", List.of(new LineItem("SKU-1", 5)));
        var result = orderService.createOrder(request);
        assertThat(result.status()).isEqualTo(OrderStatus.PENDING);
    }
}
```

## Spring Security 6
- **SecurityFilterChain:** `@Bean SecurityFilterChain` — `WebSecurityConfigurerAdapter` KALDIRILDI
- **OAuth2 Resource Server:** `spring-boot-starter-oauth2-resource-server` + JWT validation
- **Method security:** `@PreAuthorize("hasRole('ADMIN')")`, `@Secured` — endpoint seviyesinde `requestMatchers` + metod seviyesinde `@PreAuthorize`
- **CSRF:** REST API (stateless JWT) icin disable; session-based ise KAPAMA
- **Password:** `BCryptPasswordEncoder` — plain text, MD5, SHA-1 KULLANMA

## Naming Conventions
- **Packages:** tamamı kucuk harf, tekil (`com.app.order`, `com.app.inventory`)
- **Classes:** PascalCase (`OrderService`, `CreateOrderCommand`)
- **Interfaces:** PascalCase, `I` prefix KULLANMA (`OrderRepository`, `NotificationSender`)
- **Methods:** camelCase, fiil ile basla (`findByCustomerId`, `calculateTotal`)
- **Constants:** UPPER_SNAKE_CASE (`MAX_RETRY_COUNT`, `DEFAULT_PAGE_SIZE`)
- **Fields:** camelCase, `_` prefix KULLANMA (`private final OrderRepository orderRepository`)
- **Boolean:** is/has/can prefix (`isActive`, `hasStock`, `canCancel`)
- **Test methods:** snake_case veya camelCase — tutarli ol (`should_CreateOrder_When_ValidRequest`)
- **DTOs/Records:** amaç belirt (`CreateOrderRequest`, `OrderSummaryResponse`, `OrderProjection`)
- **Enums:** PascalCase, deger UPPER_SNAKE (`OrderStatus.IN_PROGRESS`)

## Anti-Pattern'ler
| Anti-Pattern | Dogru Yaklasim |
|---|---|
| Field injection (`@Autowired` field) | Constructor injection (Lombok `@RequiredArgsConstructor`) |
| N+1 query (lazy loading loop) | `@EntityGraph` veya `JOIN FETCH` |
| Checked exception her yerde | Unchecked (Runtime) exception + `@ControllerAdvice` |
| `Optional` field/parametre olarak | `Optional` sadece donus tipi |
| Fat controller (is mantigi) | Service/Use Case katmanina tasi |
| `@Transactional` controller'da | Service katmaninda; read-only icin `readOnly = true` |
| Raw SQL string concat | Spring Data query method veya `@Query` (parameterized) |
| `Thread.sleep()` test'te | Awaitility veya `@Timeout` |
| `System.out.println` | SLF4J + Logback (structured logging) |
| `new` ile service olusturma | Spring DI (`@Component`, `@Service`) |
| Generic `catch(Exception e)` | Spesifik exception + `@ExceptionHandler` |
| `Date` / `Calendar` kullanimi | `java.time` API (`Instant`, `LocalDate`, `ZonedDateTime`) |

