- **Profiling:** VisualVM, JFR (Java Flight Recorder), async-profiler
- **JPA:** Hibernate statistics (`spring.jpa.properties.hibernate.generate_statistics=true`) ile sorgu sayisini izle
- **Connection pool:** HikariCP (Spring Boot default) — `maximum-pool-size` = CPU core * 2
- **Caching:** Spring Cache abstraction + `@Cacheable` / `@CacheEvict`; provider: Caffeine (local) veya Redis
- **GC tuning:** G1GC (default); ZGC dusuk latency icin (`-XX:+UseZGC`)
